title: Ajnabee
subTitle: Raj and Priya befriend their new neighbours Vicky and Sonia. One day, Raj wakes up in Vicky's house and finds out that Sonia is killed and he is framed for it.

title: Dulhan Banu Main Teri
subTitle: Deepak, a wealthy expatriate, faces family opposition as he pursues a romance with Radha, a woman from humble origins, whilst navigating cultural expectations and class divides.

title: Dharam Adhikari
subTitle: Dharamraj, a righteous man, manages his village's affairs justly, making him well-liked among the people. Irked by his popularity, a jealous Chaudhury and Shastri conspire to get rid of him.

title: Hum
subTitle: A man is determined to kill a cruel businessman to get revenge for his father's death but is stopped by an inspector who is the mastermind behind the troubles.

title: R... Rajkumar
subTitle: Romeo, a ruffian, starts working for Shivraj, a drug lord, and they end up falling for the same girl, Chanda. Soon, a fight between the two ensues to win her over.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Kaalia
subTitle: Kallu's world shatters when his brother Shamu gets into an accident, demanding costly treatment. Desperate, he robs Shamu's employer but unfortunately lands in jail.

title: Pankh
subTitle: A young boy, dressed as a girl for a film, becomes famous. However, he struggles to break free from his breakout role after growing up, leading him to live a troubled life.

title: Colors Cineplex Bollywood
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Chaand Ka Tukda
subTitle: Determined to fulfil his mother's final wish, a young NRI returns to India to find an ideal bride. However, things take a turn after he falls in love with a village belle.

title: Sanam Bewafa
subTitle: Salman and Rukhsar's love brings two warring families face to face, only for tradition, dowry demands and heartbreak to test their fragile bond.

title: Garv: Pride and Honour
subTitle: An honest officer falls prey to a corrupt system where he is dismissed from the police force for getting involved in a murder case while trying to arrest a few corrupt politicians.

title: Hum Tumhare Hain Sanam
subTitle: Gopal is happily married to Radha until she meets her friend Suraj and starts obsessing over his singing career. Gopal suspects that they are secretly seeing each other and decides to leave her.

title: Jeet
subTitle: Karan, a gangster, falls in love with Kajal, but she marries Raju because of her father's poor health. Later, when Raju finds out about his father's illegal business, Karan is hired to kill him.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: Kris Aur Krishna
subTitle: Receiving a pray from a child's grandmother, Lord Krishna disguises himself as a young boy to rescue him who is kidnapped.

title: Fun2ssh
subTitle: Three men accidentally end up in the 10th century while being on the run. As they navigate the new world, they attempt to go back home and prove their innocence.

title: Jai Vikraanta
subTitle: When a poor, honest farmer from rural India is killed by a greedy landlord, his son, Vikraanta, takes a vow to avenge his murder.

title: Kyo Kii Main Jhuth Nahin Bolta
subTitle: Raj is a lawyer who finds great success with his countless fibs. However, when his son wishes for his father to stop lying, Raj is magically forced to speak the truth, which lands him in trouble.

title: Gharwali Baharwali
subTitle: Arun inadvertently ties the knot with Manisha and even has a child with her. He keeps this a secret from his first wife Kaajal. It is only a matter of time before his life starts to unravel.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.
